Package: RCondaRun
Type: Package
Title: Running Python code in different conda environments in one R session
Version: 0.1.0
Author: David Novak
Maintainer: David Novak <davidnovakcz@hotmail.com>
Description: Allows to source Python code and call Python functions using a specific conda environment.
    reticulate cannot switch between conda environments within one R session, but this allows you to.
Depends: reticulate, callr
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.0
